  {
    "page": 2,
    "title": "Why Avoid Cheap Dental Clinics?",
    "article": "\n<h4>1. Poor Material Quality</h4>\n<img alt=\"Why Avoid Cheap Dental Clinics?_2\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/why-avoid-cheap-dental-clinics/why-avoid-cheap-dental-clinics_2.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/why-avoid-cheap-dental-clinics/why-avoid-cheap-dental-clinics_2.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/why-avoid-cheap-dental-clinics/why-avoid-cheap-dental-clinics_2.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/why-avoid-cheap-dental-clinics/why-avoid-cheap-dental-clinics_2.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\">\n<p>Cheaper dental services often mean cheaper and unsustainable materials. Many clinics that advertise below-average costs tend to use substandard or even cheaper materials to offset treatment expenses. However, Zoom teeth whitening has been clinically tested and proven to be effective. It can whiten your teeth by up to 8 shades in just 45 minutes, while also repairing and preventing enamel damage.</p>\n</img>"
  },
  {
    "page": 3,
    "title": "Why Avoid Cheap Dental Clinics?",
    "article": "\n<h4>2. High Risk Of Complications</h4>\n<img alt=\"Why Avoid Cheap Dental Clinics?_3\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/why-avoid-cheap-dental-clinics/why-avoid-cheap-dental-clinics_3.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/why-avoid-cheap-dental-clinics/why-avoid-cheap-dental-clinics_3.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/why-avoid-cheap-dental-clinics/why-avoid-cheap-dental-clinics_3.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/why-avoid-cheap-dental-clinics/why-avoid-cheap-dental-clinics_3.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\">\n<p>Most dentists charge based on their expertise and skill level in specific treatments, so the cost often reflects their level of experience. If a dentist recommends a suboptimal treatment plan, it can lead to a range of issues, such as loose teeth, gum infections, and more.</p>\n</img>"
  },
  {
    "page": 4,
    "title": "Why Avoid Cheap Dental Clinics?",
    "article": "\n<h4>3. Limited Treatment Options</h4>\n<img alt=\"Why Avoid Cheap Dental Clinics?_4\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/why-avoid-cheap-dental-clinics/why-avoid-cheap-dental-clinics_4.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/why-avoid-cheap-dental-clinics/why-avoid-cheap-dental-clinics_4.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/why-avoid-cheap-dental-clinics/why-avoid-cheap-dental-clinics_4.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/why-avoid-cheap-dental-clinics/why-avoid-cheap-dental-clinics_4.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\">\n<p>Generally, lower-priced dental clinics offer limited, one-size-fits-all options. If your situation is more complex, this approach may pose potential risks.</p>\n</img>"
  },
  {
    "page": 5,
    "title": "Why Avoid Cheap Dental Clinics?",
    "article": "\n<h4>4. Poor Aftercare Services.</h4>\n<img alt=\"Why Avoid Cheap Dental Clinics?_5\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/why-avoid-cheap-dental-clinics/why-avoid-cheap-dental-clinics_5.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/why-avoid-cheap-dental-clinics/why-avoid-cheap-dental-clinics_5.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/why-avoid-cheap-dental-clinics/why-avoid-cheap-dental-clinics_5.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/why-avoid-cheap-dental-clinics/why-avoid-cheap-dental-clinics_5.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\">\n<p>Cheap dental clinics may see a high volume of patients daily, leaving them with no time to focus on each individual. This can result in lower standards of care.</p>\n</img>"
  },
  {
    "page": 6,
    "title": "Why Avoid Cheap Dental Clinics?",
    "article": "\n<h4>5. Limited Sedation Options For Dental Discomfort</h4>\n<img alt=\"Why Avoid Cheap Dental Clinics?_6\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/why-avoid-cheap-dental-clinics/why-avoid-cheap-dental-clinics_6.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/why-avoid-cheap-dental-clinics/why-avoid-cheap-dental-clinics_6.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/why-avoid-cheap-dental-clinics/why-avoid-cheap-dental-clinics_6.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/why-avoid-cheap-dental-clinics/why-avoid-cheap-dental-clinics_6.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\">\n<p>Fear of pain and dentists makes many patients shiver. Many affordable clinics offer limited sedatives, which may not alleviate your anxiety during procedures.</p>\n</img>"
  },
  {
    "page": 7,
    "title": "Why Avoid Cheap Dental Clinics?",
    "article": "\n<h4>6. Lack Of Cost Transparency</h4>\n<img alt=\"Why Avoid Cheap Dental Clinics?_7\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/why-avoid-cheap-dental-clinics/why-avoid-cheap-dental-clinics_7.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/why-avoid-cheap-dental-clinics/why-avoid-cheap-dental-clinics_7.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/why-avoid-cheap-dental-clinics/why-avoid-cheap-dental-clinics_7.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/why-avoid-cheap-dental-clinics/why-avoid-cheap-dental-clinics_7.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\">\n<p>To attract patients, many dental clinics advertise nearly free dental implants, subsidized by medical savings. However, you should be fully informed, as there may be hidden fees and additional costs that arise later in the treatment.</p>\n</img>"
